00060 void FusionCHPQuantificationDetectionDataTest::testRead()
00061 {
00062         FusionCHPData *chp = FusionCHPDataReg::Read("../../parsers/data/CHP_quantification_detection_file");
00063         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(chp != NULL);

00066

00070         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(sigChp->GetEntryCount() == 2);
00071         
00072         ParameterNameValueTypeList params = sigChp->GetAlgParams();
00073         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(params.size() == 1);
00074         ParameterNameValueTypeList::iterator it=params.begin();
00075         ParameterNameValueType &param = *it;
00076         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"an1");
00077         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"av1");
00078 
00079         params = sigChp->GetSummaryParams();
00080         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(params.size() == 1);
00081         it=params.begin();
00082         param = *it;
00083         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetName() == L"sn1");
00084         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(param.GetValueText() == L"sv1");
00085 
00086         affymetrix_calvin_data::ProbeSetQuantificationDetectionData e;
00087         sigChp->GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(0, e);
00088         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "abc");
00089     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.quantification == 10.0f);
00090     CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.pvalue == 0.10f);
00091         sigChp->GetQuantificationDetectionEntry(1, e);
00092         CPPUNIT_ASSERT(e.name == "xyz");
